dc_title_s: Fire and EMS Districts Monroe County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent fire districts, emergency medical service (EMS) zones, and law enforcement jurisdictions for Monroe County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NMonroe_Fire_EMS_2018.gdbN. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are NMonroe_Emergency_Medical_Service_2018N, NMonroe_Emergency_Service_Zones_2018N, NMonroe_Fire_Districts_2018N, and NMonroe_Law_Enforcement_Jurisdictions_2018N.
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_subject_sm: Fire Protection Districts, Emergency Medical Services, Law Enforcement
